=== 氣態矮行星 ===
{{See also|迷你海王星|氣態矮星}}
雖然是氣態和巨大兩個單詞的結合，但氫行星家族並不都需要像太陽系的氣態巨行星一樣的巨大。然而較小的氣態巨行星和行星，接近它們的母恆星時會比大的行星更快的流失其大氣層的質量<ref>{{cite journal | id = {{citeseerx|10.1.1.122.9085}} | title = Transonic hydrodynamic escape of hydrogen from extrasolar planetary atmospheres | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astrophysical-journal_2005-03-10_621_2/page/1049 | author1 = Feng Tian | first2 = Owen B. | last2 = Toon | first3 = Alexander A. | last3 = Pavlov | first4 = H. | last4 = De Sterck | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 621 | pages = 1049–1060 |date=March 10, 2005 |bibcode = 2005ApJ...621.1049T |doi = 10.1086/427204 }}</ref><ref>[http://arxiv.org/pdf/1001.4851 Mass-radius relationships for exoplanets], Damian C. Swift, Jon Eggert, Damien G. Hicks, Sebastien Hamel, Kyle Caspersen, Eric Schwegler, and Gilbert W. Collins</ref>。

氣態矮行星可以定義為有著由氫、氦、和其它揮發物的濃厚大氣層，和有岩石的核心，其總半徑在1.7至3.9地球半徑<ref>[http://arxiv.org/ftp/arxiv/papers/1405/1405.7695.pdf Three regimes of extrasolar planets inferred from host star metallicities] {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/ftp/arxiv/papers/1405/1405.7695.pdf |date=20151107091544 }}, Buchhave et al.</ref>。

已知最小的系外行星，可能是一顆氣態行星[[克卜勒138|克卜勒138d]]，它的質量大約是地球的60%，因此這顯示它有著濃厚的大氣層<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nature.com/news/earth-mass-exoplanet-is-no-earth-twin-1.14477 |title=Earth-mass exoplanet is no Earth twin – Gaseous planet challenges assumption that Earth-mass planets should be rocky |accessdate=2015-07-02 |archive-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107040338/http://www.nature.com/news/earth-mass-exoplanet-is-no-earth-twin-1.14477 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一顆低質量的氣態巨行星如果有適宜的溫度，仍然可以有類似氣態巨行星的半徑<ref>*[http://arxiv.org/abs/1304.5157 Mass-Radius Relationships for Very Low Mass Gaseous Planets] {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1304.5157 |date=20170914124752 }}, Konstantin Batygin, David J. Stevenson, 18 Apr 2013</ref>。

== 分類 ==
{{Main|薩達斯基太陽系外行星分類法}}
理論上，氣態巨行星可以按其建模的大氣物理特性，從其外觀分為五類：（I）氨雲、（II）水雲、（III）無雲、（IV）鹼金屬、和（V）矽雲。木星和土星都是第I類；[[熱木星|熱木星]]是IV或V。

